snippet.title: Prince Ojong
snippet.description:
I am Prince Ojong, a West African immigrant who dreams of an African renaissance. The African Nation TV is my brain child. The African Nation TV is a web channel targeting individuals and organizations of African heritage. The goal of the channel is to give a voice to our people (Africans, African-Americans, and West Indians) who have been ignored and dismissed by the dominant and lily-white media as the invisible and wretched people of the earth. By empowering our people with a big megaphone, the channel creates a network for our people to discuss our problems and find solutions. In the end, the channel will make Africa great again!

We upload a new video on Youtube weekly.

Please, join the Pan-African movement for the strong breed of the new power generation of super achievers. Feel free to call us at (240) 350-1131.

SUBSCRIBE & SHARE!

WEB SITE: http://theafricannation.com
